---
name: Onboard Check Point key-value RFC3164 syslog via UDP
description: |
  Reads Check Point syslog over UDP when firewall fields are encoded as
  pipe-delimited key-value pairs in the RFC3164 content field, and publishes
  normalized Check Point records to the topic `checkpoint`.
disabled: true
restart-on-error: 1m
---

from "{{ inputs.syslog-url }}" {
  read_syslog
}
checkpoint::syslog::parse_kv_content
publish "checkpoint"
